bossdatalist.itemdescription: NSLOCTEXT("[54BF3A7E469E551AED4655399E00A669]", "0DA2F9334F4EBD656AD6FF809CA66C8E", "A vial of shimmering green fluid said to be distilled from the sorrow of the ancient matriarch herself.
